'''唐纳德·福雷斯特·布朗'''，[[维多利亚十字勋章|VC]]（{{lang-en|Donald Forrester Brown}}，{{bd|1890年|2月23日|1916年|10月1日}}），是新西兰[[维多利亚十字勋章|维多利亚十字勋章]]得主，这是[[英联邦|英联邦]]国家（包括英国）军人作战表现英勇能够获得的最高荣誉。

布朗生于[[达尼丁|达尼丁]]，[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]爆发时在家务农。1915年下半年他自愿入伍，加入[[新西兰远征军|新西兰远征军]]飘洋过海赶赴欧洲，分到[[奥塔哥步兵团|奥塔哥步兵团]]第二营。他在[[西方戰線_(第一次世界大戰)|西方战线]]作战，1916年9月在[[弗莱尔–库尔瑟莱特之战|弗莱尔–库尔瑟莱特之战]]中表现英勇获颁维多利亚十字勋章，短短-{}-几天后就在[[勒特朗斯卢瓦之战|勒特朗斯卢瓦之战]]阵亡，勋章只能追授。布朗是新西兰远征军首位西方战线维多利亚十字勋章得主，也是全军第二位获该勋章的军人。

== 早年经历 ==
1890年2月23日，唐纳德·福雷斯特·布朗在[[紐西蘭自治領|新西兰]][[达尼丁|达尼丁]]出生<ref name="cenotaph">{{cite web | url = https://www.aucklandmuseum.com/war-memorial/online-cenotaph/record/C1726 | title = Sergeant Donald Brown | work = Auckland War Memorial Museum Cenotaph Database | accessdate = 2021-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200425193712/https://www.aucklandmuseum.com/war-memorial/online-cenotaph/record/C1726 | archive-date = 2020-04-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，父亲罗伯特·布朗（{{lang|en|Robert Brown}}）在[[奥马鲁|奥马鲁]]卖布，母亲叫杰西·麦克法兰（{{lang|en|Jessie McFarlane}}，婚后改姓布朗），两人都是苏格兰移民，在新西兰成婚并生有十个孩子<ref>{{cite web | title = Donald Forrester Brown VC | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924093400/http://www.vconline.org.uk/donald-f-brown-vc/4585996355 | url = http://www.vconline.org.uk/donald-f-brown-vc/4585996355 | website = The Comprehensive Guide to The Victoria and George Cross | accessdate = 2021-01-07 | archive-date = 2020-09-24 }}</ref>。小布朗是父母最小的儿子，先在南校学习，后就读奥马鲁的[[怀塔基男子高中|怀塔基男子高中]]。布朗完成学业后务农，1913年已在奥马鲁南部的托塔拉（{{lang|en|Totara}}）买下农场。<ref name="Oamaru">{{cite news | title = An Oamaru V.C | url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/OAM19170611.2.28 | accessdate = 2021-01-07 | newspaper = Oamaru Mail | issue = 13173 | date = 1917-06-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180923052654/https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/OAM19170611.2.28 | archive-date = 2018-09-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 第一次世界大战 ==
第一次世界大战爆发后，布朗继续务农，但一年后便转让农场，于1915年10月19日志愿加入新西兰远征军<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007">{{cite book | last1 = Harper | first1 = Glyn | last2 = Richardson | first2 = Colin | title = In the Face of the Enemy: The Complete History of the Victoria Cross and New Zealand | year = 2007 | publisher = HarperCollins Publishers | location = Auckland, New Zealand | isbn = 978-1-86950-650-6 | pages = 130–135}}</ref>。他在[[特伦特姆军营|特伦特姆军营]]受训，晋升[[下士|下士]]后于1916年1月随第九增援部队远赴[[中东|中东]]<ref name="Oamaru" />。新组建的[[新西兰师|新西兰师]]在[[埃及蘇丹國|埃及]]训练，布朗抵达后分到奥塔哥步兵团第二营。几个月后，他随[[师_(军队)|师]]前往法国投身[[西方戰線_(第一次世界大戰)|西方战线]]。<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />

新西兰军人抵达法国后前往[[阿尔芒蒂耶尔|阿尔芒蒂耶尔]]战区<ref name="Gray-2010">{{cite book | last = Gray | first = John H. | title = From the Uttermost Ends of the Earth: The New Zealand Division on the Western Front 1916–1918 | year = 2010 | publisher = Wilson Scott Publishing | location = Christchurch, New Zealand | isbn = 978-1-877427-30-5}}</ref>{{rp|48–50}}，该区战斗平缓，是新兵投身西方战线的前哨站<ref name="Gray-2010" />{{rp|59}}。第二营在阿尔芒蒂耶尔东部驻扎，虽然不及其他前线阵地战斗激烈，但仍面临大炮和狙击手的威胁<ref name="Byrne-1921">{{cite book | last = Byrne | first = A.E. | title = Official History of the Otago Regiment, N.Z.E.F. in the Great War 1914–1918 | url = http://nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-WH1-Otag.html | year = 1921 | publisher = J. Wilkie & Company | location = Dunedin, New Zealand | oclc = 978660077 | access-date = 2021-01-08 | archive-date = 2020-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200620143328/http://nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-WH1-Otag.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|93}}。第二营经常进出前线，逐渐积累[[堑壕战|堑壕战]]经验<ref name="Byrne-1921" />{{rp|93–94}}。1916年8月，新西兰师开始转移至[[索姆省|索姆省]]<ref name="Byrne-1921" />{{rp|108}}。

同年九月，已晋升[[中士|中士]]的布朗参与[[索姆河战役|索姆河攻势]]弗莱尔–库尔瑟莱特之战（{{lang|en|Battle of Flers–Courcelette}}）<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />。9月15日开战当天，奥塔哥第二营和奥克兰第二营攻占富罗森林（{{lang|fr|Bois des Foureaux}}）东南部许多德军战壕。进攻从早上6点20分开始。<ref name="McGibbon-2016">{{cite book | last = McGibbon | first = Ian | title = New Zealand's Western Front Campaign | year = 2016 | publisher = David Bateman | location = Auckland, New Zealand | isbn = 978-1-86953-926-9 | pages = 76–78}}</ref>布朗的[[连|连]]在大炮有效支持下轻松夺取第一条战壕，但在逼近下一条时侧翼遭遇猛烈机枪火力，导致多人死伤。布朗与杰西·罗杰斯（{{lang|en|Jesse Rodgers}}）下士袭击机枪据点，打死守军并夺得机枪。{{#tag:ref|罗杰斯因此役获颁[[英国军功勋章|军功勋章]]，后来[[軍官|委任]][[少尉|少尉]]，1917年7月30日[[陣亡|伤重不治]]<ref>{{cite book | last = McDonald | first = Wayne | title = Honours and Awards to the New Zealand Expeditionary Force in the Great War 1914–1918 | volume = 3 | year = 2012 | publisher = Richard Stowers | location = Hamilton, New Zealand | isbn = 978-0-473-07714-3 | page = 225}}</ref>。|group="注"}}连队其他军人重新集结并准备进攻下一道战壕。虽有大炮烟雾掩护，但他们又遇到机枪狙击，布朗等人迅速消灭据点敌兵<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />。

新西兰军人在阻碍消除后进攻，早上七点前夺下人称斯威奇战壕的德军阵地，原定协助步兵攻势的坦克始终没有出现<ref name="McGibbon-2016" />。布朗在接下来加强防御应对敌方反击的过程中发挥重要作用<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />，他发掘新战壕，以便德军炮火轰炸斯威奇战壕时己方人员躲避<ref name="McGibbon-2016" />。次日，第二营撤离前线，阵地由友军接手。布朗所在连开战当天共有180人，此时已牺牲123人<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />。

经过休整，第二营在9月28日晚返回前线，与多个营负责进攻，扫荡[[瓦尔朗库尔欧库尔|瓦尔朗库尔欧库尔]]附近的德军战壕和据点<ref name="Byrne-1921" />{{rp|133–134}}。勒特朗斯卢瓦之战（{{lang|en|Battle of Le Transloy}}）在10月1日打响，当天布朗又拿下以强大火力阻挡己方攻势的德军机枪据点。他仅携带手枪孤兵深入，打死据点德军并缴获机枪，为战友继续进攻并占领要塞创造条件。<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />但就在向逃跑的德军射击时，布朗被狙击手打中头部当场死亡<ref name="Gray-2010" />{{rp|239}}<ref>{{cite book | last = Stewart | first = H. | title = The New Zealand Division 1916–1919 | series = Official History of New Zealand's Effort in the Great War | year = 1921 | publisher = Whitcombe & Tombs | location = Auckland, New Zealand | url = http://nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-WH1-Fran.html | oclc = 2276057 | access-date = 2021-01-08 | page = 114 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201117014353/http://nzetc.victoria.ac.nz/tm/scholarly/tei-WH1-Fran.html }}</ref>。

== 维多利亚十字勋章 ==
[[File:Warlencourt_British_Cemetery_-4.JPG|thumb]]

连长认为布朗在9月15日的战斗中表现英勇，建议颁授[[杰出行为勋章|杰出行为勋章]]。第二营营长写给布朗父亲的信中表示，希望颁奖升级成[[维多利亚十字勋章|维多利亚十字勋章]]。<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />维多利亚十字勋章1856年设立，是[[大英帝国|大英帝国]]军人表现英勇的最高奖励<ref name="McGibbon-2000">{{cite book | editor-last = McGibbon | editor-first = Ian | title = The Oxford Companion to New Zealand Military History | year = 2000 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = Auckland, New Zealand | isbn = 978-0-19-558376-2}}</ref>{{rp|558–559}}。新西兰远征军高级将领起初未置可否，直到第二营军官争取提名维多利亚勋章后才行动。1917年6月12日，《[[伦敦宪报|伦敦宪报]]》刊登向布朗颁发维多利亚十字勋章的消息。<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" />授奖致辞如下：

{{Quote|感谢他在所属连队将士因机枪火力伤亡惨重时坚持进攻的勇敢和决心。这名士官带领战友冒重大个人风险抵达敌方枪口不足30码（27.4米），打死四名敌人并夺下机枪。连队继续前往，但又被机枪狙击。布朗中士再度挺身而出，胆量十足地带领战友冲向机枪阵地打死敌人。拿下第二个阵地后，连队又遭遇猛烈炮火，士官布朗临危不惧、沉着冷静，有效维持部下士气。布朗中士在接下来的进攻中无比英勇，单枪匹马冲向阻挡攻势的机枪据点，打死敌军并缴获机枪。此后，这位勇敢的军人在狙击逃敌时阵亡。|1917年6月12日《伦敦宪报》，编号30130<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=30130|supp=y|page=5866|date=1917-06-12}}</ref>}}

布朗是首位因在西方战线表现英勇获维多利亚十字勋章的新西兰远征军人，此前部队仅有[[西里尔·巴塞特|西里尔·巴塞特]]（{{lang|en|Cyril Bassett}}）因[[加里波利之战|加里波利之战]]获奖<ref name="Harper-Richardson-2007" /><ref name="McGibbon-2000" />{{rp|34}}。1917年8月30日，[[新西兰总督|新西兰总督]]、[[第二代利物浦伯爵亞瑟·福爾賈姆|第二代利物浦伯爵亞瑟·福爾賈姆]]在奥马鲁举办仪式，把维多利亚勋章交给布朗的父亲<ref>{{cite news | title = The Governor at Oamaru | url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/WDA19170830.2.24 | accessdate = 2021-01-08 | newspaper = Waimate Daily Advertiser | agency = Press Association | volume = XVII | issue = 676 | date = 1917-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180923074501/https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/WDA19170830.2.24 | archive-date = 2018-09-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。勋章由布朗的家人保留，怀塔基男子高中、[[怀乌鲁|怀乌鲁]]（{{lang|en|Waiouru}}）的[[新西兰国家陆军博物馆|伊丽莎白女王陆军纪念博物馆]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Bruce | first = David | title = 'Missing' Victoria Cross held by family | newspaper = Otago Daily News | dead-url = no | url = https://www.odt.co.nz/regions/north-otago/missing-victoria-cross-held-family | accessdate = 2021-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180923052354/https://www.odt.co.nz/regions/north-otago/missing-victoria-cross-held-family | date = 2011-12-01 | archive-date = 2018-09-23 }}</ref>，以及北奥塔哥博物馆都曾借去展出<ref>{{cite web | title = Donald Forrester Brown Victoria Cross Medal | archive-date = 2020-02-08 | dead-url = no | url = https://culturewaitaki.org.nz/north-otago-museum/exhibition/donald-forrester-brown-victoria-cross-medal | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200208133830/https://culturewaitaki.org.nz/north-otago-museum/exhibition/donald-forrester-brown-victoria-cross-medal | publisher = North Otago Museum | accessdate = 2021-01-08 }}</ref>。

布朗葬在法国瓦尔朗库尔英国公墓<ref>{{cite book | last = McGibbon | first = Ian | title = New Zealand Battlefields and Memorials of the Western Front | year = 2001 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = Auckland, New Zealand | isbn = 978-0-19-558444-8 | page = 62}}</ref>。1917年10月27日，他的纪念牌匾在奥玛鲁市议会揭幕<ref>{{cite news | title = Sergt. D.F. Brown, V.C.: Memorial Tablet Unveiled | archive-date = 2018-02-23 | dead-url = no | url = https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/OAM19171027.2.24 | accessdate = 2021-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180223171616/https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/OAM19171027.2.24 | date = 1917-10-27 | newspaper = Oamaru Mail | issue = 13291 }}</ref>。1919年，为纪念一战期间牺牲的北奥塔哥人士，奥马鲁栽下橡树<ref>{{cite web | title = North Otago Memorial Oaks | url = https://nzhistory.govt.nz/media/photo/north-otago-memorial-oaks | website = NZ History | publisher = Ministry for Culture and Heritage | accessdate = 2021-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201025164812/https://nzhistory.govt.nz/media/photo/north-otago-memorial-oaks | archive-date = 2020-10-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，[[达尼丁|达尼丁]]女王花园也有纪念布朗的牌匾<ref name="cenotaph"/>。

